info.author: Doug Hellmann
info.description:
This script uses the feedparser module to access an Atom or RSS feed and
    download the individual entries to a backup directory.  It tracks both
    etag and modified headers for each feed to reduce processing overhead.
info.name: BlogBackup
info.summary: Script to dump a blog feed to files suitable for backing up or reprocessing.
info.html_description:
This script uses the feedparser module to access an Atom or RSS feed and
download the individual entries to a backup directory. It tracks both etag and modified headers for each feed to reduce processing overhead.
